32:52.720 --> 32:53.700
 How does that work?

32:53.700 --> 32:54.780
 Is it all circuitry?

32:54.780 --> 32:56.560
 Are there chemicals involved?

32:56.560 --> 33:00.340
 What's the mechanism and when is it called into play?

33:00.340 --> 33:03.260
 But I think that's the way I tend to think about

33:03.260 --> 33:06.420
