33:16.060 --> 33:18.380
 Controlling body-wide metabolism?

33:18.380 --> 33:21.780
 Yeah, there are neurons there that respond to glucose.

33:21.780 --> 33:24.540
 When glucose goes up in your bloodstream,

33:24.540 --> 33:25.820
